        "created_at": "2014-11-02T22:36:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>But if you do a visual novel, why would you put 3D models and sprites in your scene ?<br>\nThus isnt it easier to use text type 1 and switch scenes when you need a 2D sprite on top of it ?</p>",
